        <strong>Parking:</strong> Parking is street parking. Please do not park in our neighbors’ lots. There is plenty of parking down Seventh Avenue.
      </p>
      <p class="support-page-paragraph">
        <strong>Hours of Operation:</strong> We are only open on show days, usually from 7-11 pm. You can find a calendar of upcoming shows and events <a href="/posts/">here</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="support-page-paragraph">
        <strong>Space and accessibility notes</strong> 
        Shows are held in the garage in the back. This is accessible by wheelchair with a small lip on the doorframe. The show space is heated but not cooled. 
        <br>
        Bathrooms and the front desk are located in the main house—if you need access to the house or the show space, please ring the doorbell next to the stairs. A volunteer will set up the ramp or open the front gate for you. 
        <br>
        A water fountain, earplugs, masks, and first aid supplies are available in the house. 
